os/apple/20171223/large/a0203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171223%2Flarge%2Fa0203a.gif&h=a35212a1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n湯渣 笑死<br />\n總知一有唔同意見 就撕裂"},{"pid":"e2724dc7aeedb0f02eb3e19f672aa68bf2d8c0dc","tid":507144,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"458f9b3e21398da9003e30750393d5849a0933cc","tid":507144,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩死左個女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"可能咁樣冇牽掛，放開左"}]}